role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Océanos abiertos aguas que aplastan</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Océans ouverts eaux qui écrasent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Oceanos abertos águas esmagadoras</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Открытые моря сокрушающие воды</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Oceani aperti acque che schiacciano</span></p><p begin="9.120" end="11.760" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="9.120" end="9.540">Deep</span> <span begin="9.540" end="9.940">re</span><span begin="9.940" end="10.120">gre</span><span begin="10.120" end="10.200">ts</span> <span begin="10.200" end="10.450">of</span> <span begin="10.450" end="10.850">mo</span><span begin="10.850" end="11.130">ther</span><span begin="11.130" end="11.260">s</span> <span begin="11.260" end="11.490">daugh</span><span begin="11.490" end="11.690">ter</span><span begin="11.690" end="11.760">s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">母与女儿沉入深处的悔恨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">母與女兒沉入深處的悔恨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">母たち 娘たちの深い悔い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어머니와 딸들의 깊은 후회</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Profonds regrets des mères et des filles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hondos remordimientos de madres hijas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Profonds regrets des mères et des filles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Profundos arrependimentos de mães e filhas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Глубокие сожаления матерей и дочерей</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Profondi rimpianti di madri e figlie</span></p><p begin="11.790" end="14.360" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="11.790" end="12.030">O</span><span begin="12.150" end="12.610">pen</span> <span begin="12.610" end="12.790">rif</span><span begin="12.790" end="12.870">ts,</span> <span begin="12.870" end="13.110">to</span> <span begin="13.110" end="13.390">ca</span><span begin="13.390" end="13.530">s</span><span begin="13.530" end="13.570">t</span> <span begin="13.570" end="13.920">a</span><span begin="13.920" end="14.200">drif</span><span begin="14.200" end="14.240">t</span> <span begin="14.240" end="14.360">a</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">裂隙张开 放逐一艘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">裂隙張開 放逐一艘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">裂け目を開き 漂わせる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">갈라진 틈을 열어 표류하게 하네</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Failles ouvertes pour laisser dériver</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Grietas abiertas para dejar a la deriva un</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Failles ouvertes pour laisser dériver</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Fendas abertas para lançar à deriva um</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Раскрытые разломы чтобы пустить по волнам</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Fenditure aperte per lasciare alla deriva una</span></p><p begin="14.440" end="15.750" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="14.440" end="14.750">Gho</span><span begin="14.750" end="14.830">st</span> <span begin="14.830" end="15.260">ship</span> <span begin="15.260" end="15.530">sin</span><span begin="15.530" end="15.750">king</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">正在沉没的幽灵船</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">正在沉沒的幽靈船</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">沈みゆく幽霊船を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">가라앉는 유령선</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un vaisseau fantôme qui sombre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Barco fantasma que se hunde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Un vaisseau fantôme qui sombre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Navio fantasma afundando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Корабль призрак тонет</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nave fantasma che affonda</span></p><p begin="15.780" end="17.270" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="15.780" end="16.050">A</span><span begin="16.050" end="16.350">by</span><span begin="16.350" end="16.420">s</span><span begin="16.420" end="16.650">sal</span> <span begin="16.820" end="17.120">drea</span><span begin="17.120" end="17.270">ming</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">深海梦呓</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">深海夢囈</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">深淵の夢を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">심연의 꿈</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un rêve abyssal</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sueño abisal</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Un rêve abyssal</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sonho abissal</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Бездна видит сны</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sogno abissale</span></p><p begin="17.350" end="21.510" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="17.350" end="17.550">To</span> <span begin="17.550" end="17.670">s</span><span begin="17.670" end="18.030">leep,</span> <span begin="18.030" end="18.450">to</span> <span begin="18.450" end="18.720">fall</span> <span begin="18.720" end="18.990">on</span> <span begin="18.990" end="19.200">a</span> <span begin="19.200" end="19.640">safe</span> <span begin="19.640" end="21.510">shore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">去沉睡 坠向安稳的海岸</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">去沉睡 墜向安穩的海岸</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">眠るために 安らかな岸へ倒れ込むために</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">잠들기 위해 안전한 해안에 쓰러지기 위해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dormir tomber sur une rive sûre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dormir caer en una orilla segura</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dormir tomber sur une rive sûre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Dormir cair numa margem segura</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Уснуть и упасть на безопасный берег</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dormire cadere su una riva sicura</span></p><p begin="23.270" end="24.820" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="23.270" end="23.670">Hol</span><span begin="23.670" end="23.820">ding</span> <span begin="23.820" end="24.050">a</span> <span begin="24.050" end="24.350">pa</span><span begin="24.350" end="24.620">per</span> <span begin="24.620" end="24.820">wall</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">守着一道纸墙</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">守著一道紙牆</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">紙の壁を抱きしめて</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">종이 벽을 붙잡고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je tiens un mur de papier</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sostengo un muro de papel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Je tiens un mur de papier</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Segurando uma parede de papel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Держа бумажную стену</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tengo un muro di carta</span></p><p begin="24.900" end="27.790" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="24.900" end="25.140">Buil</span><span begin="25.140" end="25.420">ding</span> <span begin="25.420" end="25.700">a</span> <span begin="25.700" end="25.980">da</span><span begin="25.980" end="26.080">mn,</span> <span begin="26.300" end="26.400">they</span> <span begin="26.400" end="26.520">are</span> <span begin="26.520" end="26.570">f</span><span begin="26.570" end="26.900">loo</span><span begin="26.900" end="27.190">ding</span> <span begin="27.190" end="27.270">the</span> <span begin="27.270" end="27.450">cir</span><span begin="27.550" end="27.720">cui</span><span begin="27.720" end="27.790">ts</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">筑起堤坝 他们却让洪流淹没回路</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">築起堤壩 他們卻讓洪流淹沒迴路</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">堤を築けば 回路は水に呑まれていく</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">댐을 쌓아도 그들은 회로를 범람시키네</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je bâtis un barrage ils noient les circuits</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Levanto un dique están inundando los circuitos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Je bâtis un barrage ils noient les circuits</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Erguendo uma barragem eles inundam os circuitos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Строя дамбу они затопляют цепи</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Costruisco una diga loro allagano i circuiti</span></p><p begin="27.800" end="29.180" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="27.800" end="27.920">To</span> <span begin="28.050" end="28.320">fin</span><span begin="28.320" end="28.420">d</span> <span begin="28.420" end="28.670">who</span> <span begin="28.670" end="28.910">I</span> <span begin="28.910" end="29.080">a</span><span begin="29.080" end="29.180">m</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只为寻回我是谁</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">只為尋回我是誰</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">わたしが誰なのかを見つけるために</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내가 누구인지 찾기 위해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pour trouver qui je suis</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Para descubrir quién soy</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Pour trouver qui je suis</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Para descobrir quem eu sou</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Чтобы найти кто я</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Per scoprire chi sono</span></p><p begin="29.460" end="33.410" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="29.460" end="29.590">Ma</span><span begin="29.590" end="29.640">ke</span> <span begin="29.640" end="29.740">a</span> <span begin="29.740" end="30.040">li</span><span begin="30.040" end="30.190">s</span><span begin="30.190" end="30.290">t,</span> <span begin="30.290" end="30.410">wri</span><span begin="30.410" end="30.440">te</span> <span begin="30.440" end="30.560">it</span> <span begin="30.560" end="30.990">down,</span> <span begin="30.990" end="31.320">in</span> <span begin="31.320" end="33.140">ti</span><span begin="33.140" end="33.260">m</span><span begin="33.260" end="33.410">e</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">列成清单 写下来 终有一日</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">列成清單 寫下來 終有一日</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">並べて 書き留めて いつか</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">목록을 만들고 적어 내려가 언젠가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Fais une liste écris la avec le temps</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Haz una lista escríbela con el tiempo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Fais une liste écris la avec le temps</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Faz uma lista escreve tudo com o tempo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Составь список запиши со временем</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Fai una lista scrivila col tempo</span></p><p begin="34.520" end="37.330" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="34.520" end="34.920">Some</span><span begin="34.920" end="35.040">time</span><span begin="35.040" end="35.100">s</span> <span begin="35.100" end="35.240">we</span> <span begin="35.350" end="35.600">nee</span><span begin="35.600" end="35.640">d</span> <span begin="35.640" end="35.870">it</span> <span begin="35.870" end="36.130">all,</span> <span begin="36.130" end="36.420">some</span><span begin="36.420" end="36.660">time</span><span begin="36.660" end="36.750">s,</span> <span begin="36.750" end="36.950">re</span><span begin="36.950" end="37.330">sign</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">有时我们渴求一切 有时只能认命</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">有時我們渴求一切 有時只能認命</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">時にすべてを求め 時に身を委ねる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">때로는 모든 것이 필요하고 때로는 체념해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Parfois il nous faut tout parfois renoncer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">A veces lo necesitamos todo a veces nos rendimos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Parfois il nous faut tout parfois renoncer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Às vezes precisamos de tudo às vezes nos rendemos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Иногда нам нужно всё иногда мы сдаёмся</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">A volte ci serve tutto a volte ci arrendiamo</span></p><p begin="37.480" end="40.390" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="37.480" end="37.620">To</span> <span begin="37.620" end="37.750">a</span> <span begin="37.750" end="38.070">worl</span><span begin="38.070" end="38.140">d</span> <span begin="38.140" end="38.380">where</span> <span begin="38.380" end="38.490">the</span> <span begin="38.490" end="38.760">cen</span><span begin="38.760" end="39.090">te</span><span begin="39.090" end="39.120">r</span> <span begin="39.120" end="39.230">i</span><span begin="39.230" end="39.370">s</span> <span begin="39.370" end="39.610">ne</span><span begin="39.610" end="39.890">ver</span> <span begin="39.890" end="40.140">a</span> <span begin="40.140" end="40.390">line</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">向着中心从不成线的世界</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">向著中心從不成線的世界</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">中心が決して線にならない世界へ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">중심이 결코 선이 아닌 세계에</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">À un monde où le centre n&apos;est jamais une ligne</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">A un mundo donde el centro nunca es una línea</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">À un monde où le centre n&apos;est jamais une ligne</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A um mundo onde o centro nunca é uma linha</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Миру где центр никогда не линия</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">A un mondo dove il centro non è mai una linea</span></p><p begin="40.760" end="45.240" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="40.760" end="40.850">Ma</span><span begin="40.850" end="40.880">ke</span> <span begin="40.880" end="41.000">a</span> <span begin="41.000" end="41.350">mo</span><span begin="41.350" end="41.500">ve,</span> <span begin="41.500" end="41.650">ta</span><span begin="41.650" end="41.680">ke</span> <span begin="41.680" end="41.790">it</span> <span begin="41.790" end="42.010">ba</span><span begin="42.010" end="42.050">ck,</span> <span begin="42.330" end="42.530">i</span><span begin="42.530" end="42.670">t&apos;s</span> <span begin="42.800" end="45.240">mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">向前一步 再夺回来 那是我的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">向前一步 再奪回來 那是我的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">踏み出して 取り戻す これはわたしのもの</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">움직이고 되돌려 빼앗아 이건 내 것이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Fais un pas reprends le il est à moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Da un paso retíralo es mío</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Fais un pas reprends le il est à moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Dá um passo volta atrás é meu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сделай шаг верни назад это моё</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Fa una moss