><span begin="3:34.570" end="3:34.870">Voi</span><span begin="3:34.870" end="3:35.070">ce</span><span begin="3:35.070" end="3:35.180">s</span> <span begin="3:35.180" end="3:35.370">tha</span><span begin="3:35.370" end="3:35.540">t</span> <span begin="3:35.540" end="3:35.980">sur</span><span begin="3:35.980" end="3:36.190">fa</span><span begin="3:36.190" end="3:36.360">ce</span> <span begin="3:36.360" end="3:36.810">seem</span> <span begin="3:36.810" end="3:37.250">to</span> <span begin="3:37.250" end="3:37.750">cal</span><span begin="3:37.750" end="3:37.780">l</span> <span begin="3:37.780" end="3:38.130">ou</span><span begin="3:38.130" end="3:38.170">t</span> <span begin="3:38.170" end="3:38.600">all</span> <span begin="3:38.600" end="3:39.060">the</span> <span begin="3:39.060" end="3:41.190">lie</span><span begin="3:41.510" end="3:41.670">s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">浮上水面的声音 仿佛唤破所有谎言</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">浮上水面的聲音 彷彿喚破所有謊言</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">浮かび上がる声が すべての嘘を呼び暴く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">수면 위로 떠오른 목소리들이 모든 거짓을 부르는 듯해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les voix qui remontent semblent dénoncer tous les mensonges</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las voces que emergen parecen denunciar todas las mentiras</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Les voix qui remontent semblent dénoncer tous les mensonges</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vozes que emergem parecem denunciar todas as mentiras</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Голоса что всплывают будто зовут всю ложь наружу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le voci che emergono sembrano gridare tutte le menzogne</span></p><p begin="3:42.100" end="3:45.490" itunes:key="L61" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:42.100" end="3:42.310">There</span><span begin="3:42.310" end="3:42.380">&apos;s</span> <span begin="3:42.380" end="3:42.630">a</span> <span begin="3:42.630" end="3:43.120">hid</span><span begin="3:43.120" end="3:43.350">den</span> <span begin="3:43.530" end="3:43.910">doo</span><span begin="3:43.910" end="3:43.960">r</span> <span begin="3:43.960" end="3:44.130">on</span> <span begin="3:44.130" end="3:44.400">the</span> <span begin="3:44.400" end="3:44.790">o</span><span begin="3:44.790" end="3:45.100">cean</span> <span begin="3:45.100" end="3:45.300">f</span><span begin="3:45.300" end="3:45.490">loor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">海底藏着一扇门</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">海底藏著一扇門</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">海の底には隠された扉がある</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">바다 밑바닥에 숨겨진 문이 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il y a une porte cachée sur le fond de l&apos;océan</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hay una puerta oculta en el fondo del océano</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Il y a une porte cachée sur le fond de l&apos;océan</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Há uma porta oculta no fundo do oceano</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Есть скрытая дверь на дне океана</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">C è una porta nascosta sul fondo del mare</span></p><p begin="3:45.520" end="3:48.470" itunes:key="L62" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:45.520" end="3:45.740">Do</span> <span begin="3:45.740" end="3:45.910">the</span><span begin="3:45.910" end="3:46.040">se</span> <span begin="3:46.040" end="3:46.650">dream</span><span begin="3:46.650" end="3:46.780">s</span> <span begin="3:46.780" end="3:47.050">be</span><span begin="3:47.050" end="3:47.430">long</span> <span begin="3:47.430" end="3:47.880">to</span> <span begin="3:47.880" end="3:48.470">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这些梦是否属于我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這些夢是否屬於我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">この夢はわたしのものなのか</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 꿈들은 내 것일까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ces rêves m&apos;appartiennent ils</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pertenecen a mí estos sueños</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ces rêves m&apos;appartiennent ils</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Será que estes sonhos pertencem a mim</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Принадлежат ли эти сны мне</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Questi sogni appartengono a me</span></p><p begin="3:49.050" end="3:57.550" itunes:key="L63" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:49.050" end="3:49.200">I</span><span begin="3:49.200" end="3:49.260">f</span> <span begin="3:49.260" end="3:49.380">it</span> <span begin="3:49.510" end="3:49.890">call</span><span begin="3:49.890" end="3:50.030">s</span> <span begin="3:50.030" end="3:50.330">my</span> <span begin="3:50.430" end="3:50.970">name,</span> <span begin="3:50.970" end="3:51.390">am</span> <span begin="3:51.390" end="3:51.880">I</span> <span begin="3:51.880" end="3:52.350">a</span><span begin="3:52.350" end="3:52.790">wa</span><span begin="3:52.790" end="3:53.380">ke</span><span begin="3:53.380" end="3:53.840">n</span><span begin="3:53.840" end="3:57.550">ing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">若它呼唤我的名字 我是否正在醒来</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">若它呼喚我的名字 我是否正在醒來</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">それがわたしの名を呼ぶなら わたしは目覚めるのか</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그것이 내 이름을 부른다면 나는 깨어나는 걸까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Si elle appelle mon nom suis je en train de m&apos;éveiller</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si llama mi nombre estoy despertando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Si elle appelle mon nom suis je en train de m&apos;éveiller</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se ela chama meu nome estou despertando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если он зовёт меня по имени пробуждаюсь ли я</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se chiama il mio nome mi sto risvegliando</span></p></div></body></tt>